English: Turkey is encircled by seas on three sides: the Aegean Sea to the west, the Black Sea to the north and the Mediterranean Sea to the south.

Pangasinan: Diad umpisay giyera kaslakan so manbiabiahe ed tapew na dayat,nen niwala so radar saray submarine so unlusong ed kaaralman na dayat pian sikaray ag nanengneng. 
English: In the beginning of the war they mostly travelled on top of the sea, but as radar began developing and becoming more accurate the submarines were forced to go under water to avoid being seen.

Pangasinan: Mas makapal nen say maria tan diad ataragey ya dalin. 
English: The submarines were very vulnerable to being seen by radar and so they had to travel under water to avoid being seen.

text: Say kakiewan et aliwan napno labat na mangroves,kabiangan so saray nalmoan ed gubat ya asakoban na Gangetic plain.

text: Impanengneng na United States GeoIogicaI Survey ed internasyonaI ya mapa na yegyeg ya angapoy yegyeg ed IceIand diad apalabas ya sakey simba.
